  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b3974538-4d39-48f2-87fe-04f59d37d42c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-aea71fdd-13b0-4ddf-818f-c9d8d6d0aa16\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-2a32278b-123e-493f-8378-e4b64abfc93b\"><b>​</b></span><span style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-c87104b0-c564-4f3a-ad17-9237ab719db2\"><b>안녕하세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-fa195cf8-d084-4afb-989d-f3b40fafb4bf\"><span style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-5ea41f3d-0430-4532-8382-119d23e7e515\"><b>평일 야간진료, 주말진료가 가능한</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-5420633d-f6ff-424d-9c19-a7d2417716e1\"><span style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#98d36c;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-875fd931-157d-42b5-8c1f-7df92d9f9de8\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-14520307-eff7-4158-ae6f-eecaa6092d42\"><b>입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-b3974538-4d39-48f2-87fe-04f59d37d42c\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d0df5662-0c01-467e-9c30-2d0e7a477278\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"7\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_7.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-92577c22-8556-400e-a544-4ff33c3637e3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-032da7e5-a16a-4efc-b93b-4456a1e6528d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-cfea6b7f-b05d-4021-9294-9d01224792fd\"><b>​</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-83229117-c933-4ac1-9a20-59f59094fc89\">당뇨병은 전 세계적으로 가장 빠르게 증가하고 있는 만성질환 중 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4641f474-8710-4033-866a-27227e185431\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-24bea486-cf9a-4df5-b34c-d3a1e5eb4b73\">하나입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2b401120-2301-4ab5-822c-29769422c162\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e9f1a6ac-80ba-4968-8b3b-b19e2e94902f\">2022년 기준, 국내 30세 이상 성인의 약 16.7%가 당뇨병 환자로 추정되며,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-30176cba-94a2-4cfe-9757-4824dab05d66\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8468c724-f494-414e-8cf5-90a485d19b71\">그 중 상당수가 초기에 자각 증상이 없거나 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-75d4ae24-ad05-42c2-bef6-9d0deb19abd2\"><b>체질적 특성으로 인해 발견이 늦어지기도</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-51535368-b929-4f16-95b0-82fd603e1828\"> 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-92577c22-8556-400e-a544-4ff33c3637e3\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-4d177f91-ef7c-4392-8273-1b985cbacf14\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4cc2a377-49ba-402d-91c4-323e2d2972fd\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-4cc2a377-49ba-402d-91c4-323e2d2972fd\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/138aa9a598a33ee5.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1600\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1600\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/138aa9a598a33ee5.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/138aa9a598a33ee5.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-4cc2a377-49ba-402d-91c4-323e2d2972fd\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f1b2c242-8f08-4aa3-8343-128df80a5b75\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b013de28-65dc-4814-bfae-401b126d3bbf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-70330c3f-d2eb-4efc-b302-9391991946fc\">한의학에서는 개인의 체질에 따라 질환 발생의 양상이 다르다고 보는데,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9a8dde07-1464-48ed-8e46-50c81962f8a3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-fddd0fb7-bace-46e9-87d9-c8b9328d8986\">그중 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-18532e20-19ad-4708-a6d9-1c89c05b90ff\"><b>소양인(少陽人)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-241971b9-2206-406d-a3aa-632b5d70b3fc\">은 당뇨병 발생 위험이 높은 체질 중 하나로 분류됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-f1b2c242-8f08-4aa3-8343-128df80a5b75\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-858ffdf0-0fa4-45b5-a0ae-c40d06f5dfb8\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-a7573282-c5c9-4c46-b25b-88ff7dfa5559\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d4011966-96e6-4c74-8e20-649af29ed24b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f613965b-b975-4fa0-94c1-62b8400394f5\"><b>소양인 특징</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-824ddf36-35c5-4d68-9d26-ef9e1b355932\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d94e0475-750c-4174-a3a3-8a09d0595b5c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ef8994cb-183b-421b-84e4-4b16b11d3ac3\"><b>상체에 열이 많고 하체가 약한 체형</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5806ca03-8215-43ae-8bc1-6768ccd57b50\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f1950bf8-4134-401e-8783-7096525448a2\">대사력이 활발하여 식욕이 왕성함</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e0d493a5-701c-4417-b429-8bb514921a8f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-cd18a616-278e-4618-91cc-0b9b4b4be91d\">소화력이 좋지만, 그만큼 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a7b32055-3c45-46fa-a513-544da6cf6082\"><b>섭취량이 많고 빠르게 허기를 느낌</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c82ac54d-3e07-41ef-a4a3-be11192cd8d0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1ddb8a7f-3ebb-4ec6-8f92-3fb2a5ffdec2\">감정기복이 크고 스트레스 반응이 빠름</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6996a99d-c700-40bc-98ac-af13bb82256b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b802ff53-96a6-4a4b-963b-ecd3f7c12763\">간 기능이 약한 경우가 많음</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f0eab846-d72b-4d70-8b31-19b46db8a360\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4a72a52f-2999-4124-b093-533bfe9383ce\">이러한 특성은 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4fd23c90-b30b-4d28-a2f6-212496a74a70\"><b>혈당을 조절하는 데 부담을 줄 수 있는 요인</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-19baf6a9-0769-4448-abca-a7af382a6c30\">으로 작용합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-824ddf36-35c5-4d68-9d26-ef9e1b355932\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-362c6bb9-0b2a-4772-ab8e-0cd996f45c0c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-ccf3136f-ee1b-4097-a16e-b04e8b2ab7cc\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a87ba33d-b8f5-4602-a031-6c94f06b2355\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e4e9bb28-9ba9-4cd1-9a22-456924585211\"><b> </b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ba332e7a-3765-457d-ad25-21d0291c2b08\"><b>소양인과 당뇨병: 어떤 연관이 있을까?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cdfd3d01-3225-4151-8636-7a01e928d412\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5b744cfb-f03f-4219-b9f3-ed2c90b5da39\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-052e7f4b-a268-4583-8ecd-b2458f3c6390\">소양인은 열이 많고 활동적인 성향 때문에 겉으로는 건강해 보일 수 있지만,</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-11659377-2a6a-477e-9e76-780a110c0624\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f6c5483c-4b7c-4973-a752-a317bb475345\"><b>체내 진액(수분) 소모가 빠르고, 간 기능이 약해 대사균형이 무너지기 쉬운 체질</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4e3eefd7-b920-4229-b996-5bb0869a8bc0\">입니다.</span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0fe024e9-1a70-411d-9053-db3dd929b8f0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f3b4008d-b433-4b88-b33f-1bbc0261839e\"><b>섭취와 대사 불균형</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0d0ad107-9cfc-4a4f-a620-43c886bcb604\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7986627e-aa2b-4640-a8e3-2a128f413b8a\"><b>스트레스 민감도</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4d239f88-389e-43a2-bced-25e87dd95c08\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-04346440-e571-4417-a869-70b38ef20293\"><b>간 기능 약화</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a4a54cc8-7dc9-4f26-b9e3-8eb3fb882990\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4fb8d81a-ebca-43ba-ab2f-0b5df3b1e04d\"><b>체열로 인한 진액 소모</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4f18ff78-2ef4-47e6-ad44-d42bd98bb9f7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-181b3e26-dff7-4c37-ae02-87767a329db3\">소양인은 쉽게 땀을 흘리고 갈증을 느껴 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9a92c89c-b6de-45f0-a1c3-61ce1de4d5d7\"><b>탈수로 인한 혈당 상승 위험</b></span></p></li></ol><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-cdfd3d01-3225-4151-8636-7a01e928d412\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-99e05e45-1033-44ce-8970-214382408fec\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-99e05e45-1033-44ce-8970-214382408fec\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bda34140e3d8292b.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1536\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1024\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bda34140e3d8292b.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bda34140e3d8292b.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"333\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-99e05e45-1033-44ce-8970-214382408fec\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-57d50249-a6c8-49c6-80ba-72ecbcf1c49b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-1ad752ff-27a1-4a8f-bd21-a57c536f16e8\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-376d74f5-b050-46ea-8346-eea9fd7e6e21\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5ccc233c-41c3-4f68-b245-6e7bd1f6c00a\"><b>이런 증상이 있다면 소양인 당뇨를 의심해보세요</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2a08d5a7-a063-4fd6-97d3-1c1f70b2db73\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8a0e0eaa-212d-4d7e-8c0b-6b36838fbc67\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-051f460f-3513-43f0-867a-a7f2685d2c7d\">식사를 해도 금방 배고픔을 느낌</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3f7065ff-e6c8-4c27-8e95-218e0b1b1285\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4264d998-3ea5-411d-9d9f-92ec9f06225d\">입이 자주 마르고 물을 많이 마심</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c44ae040-6ebf-4af3-9663-4cbe04f08594\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-52534c93-9911-442a-ba51-65c664896f52\">소변량이 늘고, 자주 화장실에 감</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-424a20f9-97cd-428d-bf13-b0646db7e285\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b38834e1-de07-43a3-8ada-8a6b58fe6754\