                     <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-37d22391-8848-43d3-9dbe-790acfd8375a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4d55a62d-3099-4497-8133-4059bc5da0c6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7a75066d-d60b-4604-9fd6-5afbb8cc9d49\">당뇨병은 단순히 혈당 수치의 문제가 아니라, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bcff9fd1-a37d-4ac2-8061-09af1b7f5d44\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9ad2c446-f04d-456c-9333-679a703c178b\"><b>생활습관과 체질이 복합적으로 작용하는 질환</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-85a1d99b-c733-428e-b708-963d0007f36e\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ccadaced-a45f-46de-97b8-c397764a7e75\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-70a20fdb-91cd-4c92-966b-0ee6165e4749\">소양인처럼 겉은 건강해 보이지만 내면의 대사 불균형을 지닌 체질은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b5bbf1df-ba36-483c-878a-76b9bd9f832e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9e3b41ea-e150-4bc9-bd3e-ccfd49ecd92d\"><b>증상이 드러나기 전부터 예방과 관리를 시작하는 것이 매우 중요합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f2a6b6ac-048e-48d8-96e5-3f6c9cff39c7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-09c045c7-0a69-4d37-8403-cef283c012e0\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2d0c51e9-3f14-4918-8fa8-7d25708024ea\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-5b2abdb4-e4a7-4d3b-bce2-ad58247b26eb\">내 체질에 맞는 한의학적 접근으로 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7be540f7-30c0-42be-bf6a-c96eede88f1f\"><b>건강한 혈당 밸런스</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0d1e35c9-51ef-4da6-8361-165d572d7720\">를 유지해보세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d401035c-321c-49b1-afb8-e64b39c68399\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d1afbf5e-596e-41de-bf6f-3f62af2a274a\">정확한 체질 진단과 상담이 필요하다면 </span><span style=\"background-color:#98d36c;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-77e118a2-48b4-4d3a-9928-c8a32ec36f0b\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ec3f6051-1be4-4e3e-a50d-03bfcf668e73\">에 내원하여 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f6cc7c09-354c-4837-9500-03e9b2b65f78\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e85b0ab3-e640-4e63-b704-c32f87c69ea8\">도움을 받으시길 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-37d22391-8848-43d3-9dbe-790acfd8375a\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d61a879e-bc73-40a2-8be1-223db8b6e25e\">\n                    <div class=\"